Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有女士在场你不能骂人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You shouldn't swear. There's ladies present.
