Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人   我叫爱德华.布鲁...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Ma'am, my name is Edward Bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...有些人要看看你的眼睛\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and there's some folks like to see your eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那拿到那个了? -我带来了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- You get The Eye? - I brought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们看看\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let's see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇   救命!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Whoa, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见自己怎么死的了. 我摔下来  不行了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I saw how I was gonna die. I was old and I fell.
