Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是   一方面   如果你想的都是死...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I mean, on one hand, if dying was all you thought about...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...它就会搅乱你的生活\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...it could kind of screw you up.
