Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为   其他的所有情况下   你知道你会得救\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Because, everything else, you'd know you could survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的是我想知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I guess I'm saying I'd like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎么死的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's how I go.
