Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不是本耐特大夫的车? \N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Is that Dr. Bennett's car? 
