Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他怎么样? -不   我来吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- And how is he? - Well... No, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没救了. 不吃东西. 因为没吃东西  所以越来越虚弱\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's impossible. He won't eat. Because he doesn't eat, he's weaker.
