Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:14:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他还剩多少日子? -你现在不能说这个\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- How much time does he have left? - You don't talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到时间\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威尔\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本耐特大夫. 哦   很高兴见到你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Dr. Bennett. Oh, it's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妻子   傑瑟芬\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}My wife, Josephine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很荣幸见到你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-有7个月了 -离那个日子!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- You're seven months. - To the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个男孩\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着让他喝点什么. 即使他不要也要试着让他喝\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Try to get him to drink one of these. He won't, but go ahead and try.
