Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不用走\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This is not how I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真的? -实际上. 我从那个眼睛里看到了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Really? - Truly. I saw it in The Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沼泽旁的那个老女人? -她是个女巫\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- The old lady by the swamp? - She was a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不   她只是有点老\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No, she was old and probably senile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从那只眼睛里看到我是怎么死的   但现在好像不是这样子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I saw my death in that eye, and this isn't how it happens.
