Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:17:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的结局. 我不想破坏气愤\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Surprise ending. Wouldn't want to ruin it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈说你我没机会再说话了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Your mother thought we wouldn't talk again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看我们.现在聊的多好\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Look at us. We're talking fine.
