Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.31,0:57:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爱德华.布鲁. 我要和你谈谈\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's Edward Bloom. I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.82,0:57:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛维先生?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mr. Calloway?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.35,0:58:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不. 等等!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No. Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.87,0:58:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上   我发现你认为邪恶的东西...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That night, I discovered that most things you consider evil or wicked...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.38,0:58:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...只是出於孤独或者是缺乏社交上的分寸\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...are simply lonely and lacking in social niceties.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.92,0:59:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没杀死什么东西   是吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Didn't kill anything, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.92,0:59:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几只兔子而已. 不过我认为其中一只本来就是死的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A few rabbits. But I think one of them was already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.43,0:59:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得我有点消化不良\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That would explain the indigestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.94,0:59:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.94,0:59:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看错你了   孩子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I was wrong about you, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.95,0:59:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也许什么长处   但是其实你有的   而且很多\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You may not have much, but what you got, you got a lot of.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.95,0:59:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能追到那姑娘\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You could get any girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.45,0:59:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想要一个\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's only one I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.96,0:59:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.96,0:59:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...叫桑德拉.坦浦顿\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...is Sandra Templeton.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.97,0:59:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了奥本念书\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}She goes to Auburn.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.97,0:59:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学期快结束了   所以你最好快点\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Semester's almost over, so you better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.48,1:00:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  谢谢你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.98,1:00:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-祝你好运   孩子! -谢谢你   先生!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Good luck, kid! - Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.08,1:00:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-再见 -再见   爱德华.\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Bye, now. - Bye, Edward.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.16,1:00:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说完再见   我换了三趟火车...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}After saying my goodbyes, I hopped three trains...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.67,1:00:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...在下午到了奥本大学\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...to get to Auburn that afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.20,1:01:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不认识我   我叫爱德华.布鲁...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You don't know me, but my name is Edward Bloom...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.20,1:01:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...我爱你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.21,1:01:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了三年工就是为了知道你是谁\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've spent the last three years working to find out who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.21,1:01:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有几次我被枪打中  被刀刺伤 \N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've been shot, stabbed, and trampled a 
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.39,1:01:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被踩过   我的肋骨断了两次\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}few times. I broke my ribs twice.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.72,1:01:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能够见到你我认为一切都是值得的...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But it's all been worth it to see you here now...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.22,1:01:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...最后能和你说话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and to finally get to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.22,1:01:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我要娶你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Because I'm destined to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.22,1:01:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我在马戏团见到你的第一刻起我就知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I knew it when I saw you at the circus, and I know it now more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.23,1:01:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-对不起 -你不必道歉\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I'm sorry. - You don't have to apologize to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.23,1:01:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你今天所看见的最幸运的人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm the luckiest person you'll find today.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.24,1:01:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不   对不起我不想结婚\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No, I'm sorry I'm engaged to be married.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.25,1:01:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你错了.我真的瞭解你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But you're wrong. I do know you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.75,1:01:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少听过你的名声\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}At least by reputation.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.75,1:02:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从阿斯顿来的爱德华.布鲁\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Edward Bloom from Ashton.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.25,1:02:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧   实际上我已经和从阿斯顿来的丹.普来斯定婚了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}See, I'm actually engaged to a boy from Ashton. Don Price.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.76,1:02:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他比你大一点\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He was a few years older than you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.27,1:02:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么....\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.28,1:02:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.28,1:02:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰你很抱歉\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm sorry to have bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.29,1:02:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停! 并不有趣\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Stop it! It's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.29,1:02:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的孩子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That poor boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.79,1:02:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运总是残酷地捉弄着你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Fate has a cruel way of circling around on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.30,1:02:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易离开了阿斯顿...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}After all this work to leave Ashton...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.30,1:02:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...我爱的姑娘却和那来的人定了婚\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...the girl I love was now engaged to one of its biggest jerks.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.30,1:02:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人斗争的时候了...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's a time when a man needs to fight...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.31,1:03:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...他需要接受使命落空的情况...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and a time when he needs to accept that his destiny's lost...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.31,1:03:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,... 船起航了   傻瓜才会向前\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...the ship has sailed, and that only a fool will continue.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.31,1:03:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上   我一直是个傻瓜\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Truth is, I've always been a fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.82,1:03:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑德拉.坦浦顿   我爱你   我要娶你!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sandra Templeton, I love you, and I will marry you!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.41,1:03:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你看到的   如果这些规则适用我们的生活...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So as you can see, if we apply these rules to our everyday life...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.33,1:03:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...供求更有意义\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...supply and demand makes much more sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.33,1:03:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看下一张图  引入这一点将会更有说服力--\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Take a look at the next graph, and the import of this will be even stronger...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.34,1:03:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--三个小时\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- for three hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.85,1:03:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.66,1:04:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-水仙! -这是你最喜欢的花\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Daffodils! - They're your favorite flower.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.16,1:04:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪里去弄来这么多?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How did you get so many?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.66,1:04:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我5个州都打了电话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I called everywhere in five states.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.66,1:04:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉他们这是我娶妻的唯一方法\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I told them it was the only way to get my wife to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.67,1:04:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎不瞭解我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You don't even know me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.17,1:04:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用余生去瞭解\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I have the rest of my life to find out.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.67,1:04:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑德拉!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sandra!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.68,1:04:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是丹. 答应我别伤害他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's Don. Promise you won't hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.68,1:04:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是你想要的  我发誓\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If that's what you want, I swear to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.18,1:04:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-布鲁? -丹\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Bloom? - Don.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.69,1:04:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干什么? 她是我的女孩. 我的!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What the hell are you doing? This is my girl. Mine!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.19,1:04:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没注意到她已经名花有主了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I wasn't aware that she belonged to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.70,1:04:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了? 难道你害怕得不敢还击了?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What's the matter? Are you too scared to fight back?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.20,1:05:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓我不会\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I promised I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.70,1:05:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.70,1:05:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹   停!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don, stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.71,1:05:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我被揍的很惨   但是最后输的却是丹.普来斯\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}While I took the beating of a lifetime, Don Price was ultimately defeated.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.71,1:05:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力过猛使得他天生的心脏瓣膜缺陷恶化\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All the physical activity had worsened a congenital valve defect.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.72,1:05:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说   他的心脏还不够强壮\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Put simply, his heart wasn't strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.73,1:05:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹! 我不会嫁给你的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don! I will never marry you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.73,1:05:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 你是说   你爱这个傢伙?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What? You mean, you love this guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.73,1:05:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是个陌生人   但我喜欢他胜过你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's almost a stranger, and I prefer him to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.26,1:06:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后   桑德拉仍然在同一天去了教堂\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}As it turned out, Sandra was able to keep her same date at the chapel.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.77,1:06:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是新郎换了人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Only the groom had changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.77,1:06:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你说过你没有在教堂举行过婚礼\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I thought you said you didn't have a church wedding.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.78,1:06:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都好了  但是还有点麻烦\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We were all set to, but there was a complication.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.78,1:06:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这药会让你口渴吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Is it the medicine that's making you thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.79,1:06:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上   这一直很口渴\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Truth is, I've been thirsty my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.79,1:06:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Never really known why.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.80,1:06:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我11岁的时候....\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There was a time when I was 11...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.80,1:06:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在谈你的婚礼\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You were talking about your wedding.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.30,1:06:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有忘记.我绕着弯在讲话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I didn't forget. I was just working on a tangent.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.80,1:06:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道   大多数人说话都很直接\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You see, most men, they'll tell you a story straight through.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.31,1:06:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样并不複杂  但是也很没趣\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It won't be complicated, but it won't be interesting, either.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.81,1:07:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你的故事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I like your stories.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.89,1:07:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And I like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.81,1:07:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你在马戏团工作的时候   你没有一个固定的地址\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, when you work for the circus, you don't have a regular address.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.82,1:07:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年后  有很多信我没收到\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So after three years, there was a lot of undelivered mail.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.82,1:07:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我住院的四周时间里...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}During the four weeks I was in the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.82,1:07:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...邮差终於找到了我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...the postmaster finally caught up with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.33,1:07:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管我的心也许是属於桑德拉的...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And it seems that while my heart belonged to Sandra...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.83,1:07:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...我身体的其它部分则属於美国政府\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...the rest of my body belonged to the U.S. government.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.85,1:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时在军中服役期最长可达三年...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A hitch in the Army was up to three years at that point...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.86,1:07:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...而我已经等了三年才见到桑德拉...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and having waited three years just to meet Sandra...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.86,1:07:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...我知道我没有办法离开她这么久时间\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...I knew I couldn't survive being away from her that long.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.86,1:07:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就接那种危险的任务...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So I took every hazardous assignment I could find...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.36,1:08:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...希望能把我的时间缩短一年也好\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...with the hope of getting my time down to less than a year.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.87,1:08:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上! 上!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.87,1:08:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我接到个秘密行动...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}When I was offered a secret mission...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.88,1:08:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...要我偷王开堂发电厂的图纸...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...to steal the plans for the Wong Kai Tang power plant...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.38,1:08:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...我跳了下去报效祖国\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...I jumped at the chance to serve my country.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.89,1:08:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上! 上!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.50,1:09:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 兄弟 兄弟 什么乱七八糟的 下台吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.35,1:09:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这傢伙谁找的 真他妈要枪毙
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.54,1:09:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很漂亮的小姐为我们演出
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.80,1:09:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩有时会感觉孤独
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.66,1:09:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有爱人来爱她
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.42,1:09:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候孤独难耐
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.43,1:09:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她内心要爆发
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.61,1:10:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到一个男人就抓紧 扯去他的衣衫
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.98,1:10:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可她不会.她不能
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.49,1:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她需要一个特殊 非凡 超群的男人
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.10,1:10:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那与我一般容貌的女孩
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.95,1:10:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想要得到 可她有需要
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.50,1:10:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁有需要?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Any of you got needs?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.92,1:10:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有过双重的冒险
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.73,1:10:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我流过双倍的泪
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.99,1:10:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在一半的岁月中有过双倍的不幸
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.31,1:10:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我需要一个男人
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.85,1:10:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有着加倍的意志
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.94,1:10:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要这样的男人
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.92,1:10:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为宝贝  我有双倍的爱要付出
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.40,1:11:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要这样的男人
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.99,1:11:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为宝贝 我有双倍的爱要付出
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.59,1:12:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么每次都错过暗示?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How could you miss your cue?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.10,1:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我在那一个人看上去像个傻瓜\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You make me look like a fool out there alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.10,1:12:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一个人!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You weren't alone!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.10,1:12:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是谁?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.10,1:12:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会伤害你的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm not going to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.11,1:12:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当然不敢\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Damn right you're not.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.61,1:12:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守卫!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}GUARD!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.11,1:12:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打扰我们!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tell your men not to bother us!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.11,1:12:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把门帘关上!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And close that curtain!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.12,1:12:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你帮忙\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Please, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.12,1:12:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道我们能帮你?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What makes you think we'll help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.13,1:12:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来一小时   我要向桑德拉.坦普顿表白...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Over the next hour, I described my love for Sandra K. Templeton...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.13,1:12:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...是我经历的苦难让我出现在她们面前\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and the ordeal that brought me before them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.14,1:12:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像以往一样  这份爱拯救了我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}As it had always been, this love was my salvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.14,1:12:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命中注定的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It was destined to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.14,1:13:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们制定了一个周密的逃跑计划...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We put together an elaborate plan for escape...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.65,1:13:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...包括乘捕鲸船去俄国...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...involving a whaling ship to Russia...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.15,1:13:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...然后乘游艇去古巴   再坐一艘又小又髒的独木舟到达迈阿密\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...a barge to Cuba, and a small, dirty canoe to Miami.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.15,1:13:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都知道这很危险\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We all knew it would be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.15,1:13:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去了美国可以做点什么呢?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And what are we supposed to do when we get to America?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.16,1:13:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你们安排的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I can get you bookings.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.16,1:13:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识娱乐圈的大人物\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I know the biggest man in show business.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.66,1:13:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲍勃?!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Bob Hope?!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.16,1:13:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比他大牌\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Bigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.17,1:13:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.17,1:13:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和双胞胎开始了我们的坚信旅程...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And so the twins and I began our arduous journey...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.18,1:13:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...绕了半个地球\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...halfway around the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.18,1:13:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸的是   没有办法可以发消息回美国\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Unfortunately, there was no way to send a message back to America.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.68,1:13:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料军方以为我战死沙场了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And so it was no surprise that the Army believed I was dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.20,1:14:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不   天哪!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No, God!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.20,1:14:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个月后   桑德拉一直做着恶梦\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}After four months, Sandra had gotten over the worst of the nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.21,1:14:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当电话铃响的时候   她不知道打电话来的是我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}When the phone rang, she didn't think it was somehow me calling her.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.21,1:14:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当车开过的时候   她没有起身开窗看\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}When a car drove past, she didn't get up to check out the window.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.25,1:14:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你父亲昨天在谈\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I talked with your father last night.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.76,1:15:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从没有告诉我你父母是如何相遇的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You never told me how your parents met.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.26,1:15:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是在奥本大学认识的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They met at Auburn.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.26,1:15:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细节怎么样呢? 他们怎么坠入爱河的?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What about the details? How they fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.27,1:15:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马戏团. 战争\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The circus. The war.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.27,1:15:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些你从来没告诉过我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You never told me any of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.27,1:15:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大多数的事没发生过\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's because most of it never happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.27,1:15:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很浪漫\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But it's romantic.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.78,1:15:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么? -什么   比起和一个法国女人争吵浪漫...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- What? - What, I know better...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.78,1:15:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...我知道的更多\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...than to argue romance with a French woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.28,1:15:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爱你的父亲吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do you love your father?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.79,1:15:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都爱自己的父亲 他很招人喜欢\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Everyone loves my father. He's a very likable guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.79,1:15:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爱他吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do you love him?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.30,1:15:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须理解\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You have to understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.30,1:15:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我长大的时候   他出去的时间比在家时间多\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}When I was growing up, he was gone more than he was there.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.30,1:15:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就开始想他是不是在其他地方过着另外的生活\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And I started thinking maybe he's got this second life somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.31,1:16:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外的家庭   另外的房子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Another family, another house.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.31,1:16:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他离开我们去他们那\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And he leaves us and goes to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.81,1:16:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者   或者....\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Or, or...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.82,1:16:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者没有第二个家庭. 可能他不想要个家\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Or maybe there is no second family. Maybe he never wanted a family.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.32,1:16:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样   他喜欢他另外的生活和讲故事...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Whatever it is, he likes his second life better and he tells his stories...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.83,1:16:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...因为他不甘忍受这个无聊的地方\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...because he can't stand this boring place.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.33,1:16:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-但那不是真的. -那么   什么是真的?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- But it's not true. - Well, what's true?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.33,1:16:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他从来没有说过真话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's never told me a single true thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.34,1:16:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看   嘿....\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Look, hey...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.34,1:16:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你为什么喜欢他了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I know why you like him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.34,1:16:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道为什么每个人都喜欢他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I know why everyone likes him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.85,1:16:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要告诉你  我没有疯\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But I need you to tell me that I'm not crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.35,1:16:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你没有\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.35,1:16:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你应该和他谈谈\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And I think you should talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.36,1:16:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉里.普凯特的雪佛莱让客人这么说\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Larry Puckett's Chevrolet lets the customer do the talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.36,1:17:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉里.普凯特的通用车在车厂做担保\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Larry Puckett's GM-certified vehicles are under factory warranty.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.37,1:17:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以最多比生产者建议零售价少付40%\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And you can save up to 40 percent off the original MSRP.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.87,1:17:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我有跟你讲过--? -有\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Did I ever tell you about...? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.38,1:17:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫树和别克的故事? 我们听过\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The maple tree and the Buick? We've heard it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.38,1:17:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有人没听过\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I know someone who hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.39,1:17:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那-- -树倒在车上  把糖浆洒了一地\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- The... - Tree fell on the car, spilling the syrup.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.89,1:17:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引来了很多苍蝇  沾在车上...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Which attracted the flies, which got stuck to it...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.39,1:17:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...飞走时带上整个车\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and flew off with the whole car.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.40,1:17:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真实的故事是我怎么开走这车\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But the real story is how I got the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.40,1:17:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你知道的-- -父亲?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- You see... - Dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.91,1:17:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Son.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.41,1:17:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能谈谈吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Can we talk?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.91,1:17:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我该去洗盘子了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I think I'll get started on these dishes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.41,1:17:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.43,1:18:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你知道冰山吗  爸爸? -我?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- You know about icebergs, Dad? - Do I?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.43,1:18:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看过一次\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I saw an iceberg once.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.43,1:18:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们当时正把它拉到德克萨斯州当饮用水\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They were hauling it down to Texas for drinking water.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.94,1:18:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他们没想到里面还冻了一头大象\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They didn't count on there being an elephant frozen inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.94,1:18:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-长毛的那种.毛象 -爸爸!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- The woolly kind. A mammoth. - Dad!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.44,1:18:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.95,1:18:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是打个比方\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm trying to make a metaphor here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.45,1:18:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不应该用提问的方式开始...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, you shouldn't have started with a question...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.45,1:18:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...因为人们喜欢回答问题\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...because people want to answer questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.45,1:18:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能从"关於冰山的是...."开始\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You should've started with, "The thing about icebergs is..."
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.46,1:18:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好. 关於冰山的问题是你只看了10%\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Okay, okay. The thing about icebergs is you only see 10 percent.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.96,1:18:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水下的90%你没看见\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The other 90 percent is below the water where you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.46,1:18:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And that's...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.47,1:18:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...那是和你有关的   爸爸\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...what it is with you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.47,1:18:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只看出了一点...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I am only seeing this little bit...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.47,1:18:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...就是在水面上的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...that sticks above the water.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.47,1:19:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦   你只看见我鼻子下的? 我的下巴?我的--\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, you're only seeing down to my nose? My chin? My...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.98,1:19:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸   我不知道你是...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Dad, I have no idea who you are...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.98,1:19:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...因为你没告诉过我什么真相\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...because you've never told me a single fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.48,1:19:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉了你几千个真相  \N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've told you a thousand facts,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.14,1:19:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威尔. 这就是我干的  讲故事!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&} Will. That's what I do, I tell stories!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.49,1:19:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说...谎   爸爸\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You tell... lies, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.49,1:19:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是说那些有趣的谎言\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You tell amusing lies.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.49,1:19:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些就是你在一个5岁孩子临睡前讲的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Stories are what you tell a 5-year-old at bedtime.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.99,1:19:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你的儿子长到10  15  20  30岁时...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They're not elaborate mythologies that you maintain...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.50,1:19:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...你就不能再编织那些动人的神话了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...when your son is 10 and 15 and 20 and 30.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.50,1:19:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And I believed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.50,1:19:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就不应该相信你的故事了  但我信了很久\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I believed your stories so much longer than I should have.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.01,1:19:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我意识到你说的是不可能的...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Then when I realized everything you said was impossible...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.01,1:19:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...我感觉自己想个傻瓜一样相信你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...I felt like a fool to have trusted you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.51,1:19:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就像圣诞老人和复活节兔子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're like Santa Claus and the Easter Bunny.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.02,1:19:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很动人  但也很虚假\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Just as charming and just as fake.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.02,1:19:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我虚假\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You think I'm fake.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.52,1:19:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在表面上  爸爸 但都是我看见的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Only on the surface, Dad. But it's all I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.53,1:19:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.53,1:19:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm about to have...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.53,1:20:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...我有自己的孩子了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...a kid of my own.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.03,1:20:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你在一生都没能理解我...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It would kill me if he went through his whole life...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.04,1:20:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...我会很难过\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...never understanding me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.54,1:20:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会难过   恩?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It would kill you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.54,1:20:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要什么   威尔? 你想成为谁?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What do you want, Will? Who do you want me to be?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.55,1:20:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Just yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.05,1:20:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好   坏   让我看看真实的你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Good, bad, everything. Just show me who you are for once.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.05,1:20:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自出生以来我一直是我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've been nothing but myself since the day I was born.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.55,1:20:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你看不见   是你的失败   不是我的!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And if you can't see that, it's your failing, not mine!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.09,1:21:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲决定自己要间办公室...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Your father decided that he needed to have an office...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.09,1:21:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...当然   在家是不行的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and, of course, it wouldn't do to have it in the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.59,1:21:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么....\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.60,1:21:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该比我更瞭解什么是重点\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You'll know better than me what's important.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.61,1:21:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.11,1:21:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战争期间\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It was during the war.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.12,1:21:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲失踪了 他们以为他已经牺牲\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Your father went missing. They thought he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.12,1:21:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦   真的是这样吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Oh, that really happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.62,1:21:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲说的不完全是编造的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Not everything your father says is a complete fabrication.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.13,1:21:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我要去看看他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I think I'll go check on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.63,1:21:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要躺会\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I need to lie down for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.14,1:21:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好   去吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Okay, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.65,1:22:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争以后  阿拉巴马的孩子们回到家园找工作\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}After the war, the sons of Alabama returned home, looking for work.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.66,1:22:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都比我有优势\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Each had the advantage over me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.16,1:22:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们或者   而我已经被官方证实死亡\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They were alive, while I was officially deceased.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.16,1:22:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前途渺茫...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}With my prospects few...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.16,1:22:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...我找了一份适合自己的旅游推销工作\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...I took a job as a traveling salesman. It suited me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.67,1:22:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以说爱德华 布鲁...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If there was one thing you can say about Edward Bloom...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.17,1:22:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...是个社交人物\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...it's that I am a social person.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.67,1:22:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-恭喜 -谢谢   险胜\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Congratulations. - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.18,1:22:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每次都要出去几周\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I could be gone for weeks at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.18,1:22:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是每个星期五   我把钱都...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But every other Friday, I put all the money I made...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.18,1:22:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...存入一个帐号...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...into an account set aside for a proper house...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.68,1:22:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...用来买白色栅栏的房子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...with a white picket fence.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.69,1:22:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想借此机会向大家介绍我们的新产品...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'd like a moment of your time to tell you about my new product...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.70,1:23:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...自动手\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...the Handi-matic.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.71,1:23:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几年后   我在其他城市做不同的商品...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A few years later, I added other products and other cities...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.72,1:23:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...直到我的领地从沿海地区延伸到西部的德州\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...until my territory stretched from the coast to western Texas.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.24,1:23:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Edward?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.74,1:23:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华 布鲁!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Edward Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.74,1:23:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我   诺什.温斯勒\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's me, Norther Winslow.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.75,1:23:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.75,1:23:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很惊讶竟然远在德州...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I was astonished to see the greatest poet of both Ashton and Spectre...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.25,1:24:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...看到了阿斯顿和幽灵镇两地最伟大的诗人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...all the way out in Texas.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.25,1:24:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你知道   当你离开幽灵镇的时候  我的眼界开阔了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I want you to know, when you left Spectre, it opened my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.26,1:24:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的生活我还没有体验过呢\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There was a whole life out there that I was not living.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.76,1:24:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也出来了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So I traveled.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.76,1:24:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了法国  非洲  半个南美\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I saw France, Africa, half of South America.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.77,1:24:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都有新的经历. 这是我的格言\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Every day, a new adventure. That's my motto.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.77,1:24:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了   诺什. 我为你感到高兴\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's great, Norther. I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.27,1:24:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在干什么?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What are you doing now?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.77,1:24:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要抢劫这个地方\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm robbing this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.28,1:24:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  所有人蹲下!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All right, everybody down!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.78,1:24:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿! 把枪滑过来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hey! Just slide that over.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.29,1:24:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你能不能把它拿过来? -什么?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Would you mind grabbing that? - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.79,1:24:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.80,1:24:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会拿光现金抽屉里的钱...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm gonna be cleaning out the cash drawers...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.80,1:24:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...而我的助手会去金库\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and my associate here is gonna handle the vault.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.31,1:25:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了   你! 你当我的助手   好吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All right, you! You help my friend, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.31,1:25:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.83,1:25:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起   女士 是我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm sorry, ma'am. I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.83,1:25:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不想任何人受伤\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I really just don't want anyone to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.34,1:25:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.84,1:25:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是....\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's just...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.35,1:25:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没钱\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's no money.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.85,1:25:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们完全破产了. 不要告诉任何人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We're completely bankrupt. Don't tell anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.85,1:25:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果储蓄和贷款的钱早已被洗劫一空...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It turned out that the Savings & Loan had already been robbed...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.86,1:25:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...不是被持枪的强盗  而是被德州的地产投机商抢走的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...not by armed bandits, but by speculators in Texas real estate.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.86,1:25:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了   我们走!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.87,1:26:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺什!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Norther!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.39,1:26:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对! 这里有$400!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Yeah! There's gotta be close to $400 here!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.40,1:26:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还只是抽屉里的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And that's just from the drawers.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.90,1:26:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来看看你从金库里拿了多少\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let's see what you got from the vault.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.41,1:26:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点吗? 整个金库里?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This is it? The whole vault?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.41,1:26:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.92,1:26:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的存款单\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's got your deposit slip on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.42,1:27:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想让你空手而归\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, I just didn't want you leaving empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.42,1:27:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情你应该知道. 他们没钱的理由....\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's something you should know. The reason they don't have money...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.43,1:27:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉诺什德州石油价格难以预计的变化...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I told Norther about the vagaries of Texas oil money...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.93,1:27:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...还有房地产价格效应...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and its effect on real-estate prices...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.93,1:27:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...以及信託程序的不严格执行...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and how lax enforcement of fiduciary process...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.44,1:27:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...已经使得储蓄和贷款减少\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...had made savings and loans particularly vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.44,1:27:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了这个  诺什留下了个结论:\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hearing this news, Norther was left with one conclusion:
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.44,1:27:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该去华尔街. 钱都在那里\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I should go to Wall Street. That's where all the money is.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.95,1:27:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我犯罪的日子已经结束了...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I knew then that while my days as a criminal were over...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.45,1:27:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的帮忙!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Thanks for the hand!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.95,1:27:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...诺什开始了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...Norther's were just beginning.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.95,1:27:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当诺什赚到了他的第一个100万时...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}When Norther made his first million dollars...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.46,1:27:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...他给了我10  000的支票\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...he sent me a check for 10,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.96,1:27:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝了   但他说这是他付给我的职业咨询费\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I protested, but he said it was my fee as his career advisor.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.46,1:27:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些钱足以给我的妻子买一栋有白色...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It was enough to buy my wife a proper house...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.96,1:27:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,... 栅栏的房子\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...with a white picket fence.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.97,1:27:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是男人对财富的最大梦想\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And for that, it was all the riches a man could ever want.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.00,1:28:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我乾透了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I was drying out.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.50,1:28:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.01,1:28:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看我们该给你买个洒水器...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I think we ought to get you a plant mister...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.01,1:28:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...那样我们就可以像浇花一样给你浇水了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...so we can just spray you like a fern.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.04,1:29:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Come, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.55,1:29:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我是永远不会干透的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't think I'll ever dry out.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.10,1:30:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿着. 我看看....\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You carry on. I'll see...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.11,1:30:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.11,1:30:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你是珍尼佛.希尔? -我是\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Are you Jennifer Hill? - I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.12,1:30:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是威尔吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And you're Will.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.62,1:30:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看过你的照片. 所以我认的出你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've seen a picture of you. That's how I recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.12,1:30:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着   肯尼   我们今天可不可以不要上了?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Listen, Kenny, why don't we skip the lesson today?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.13,1:30:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周再上\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We can go again next week.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.63,1:30:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把这个换给妈妈吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do I have to give it back to my mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.13,1:30:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想说就不要说了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, I won't tell her if you won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.73,1:31:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么认识我父亲的?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How did you know my father?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.81,1:31:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他去推销的必经之地...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, this was on his sales route...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.81,1:31:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...他经常经过这里  每个人都认识他\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...so he was through here all the time, and everyone in town knew him.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.32,1:31:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有事吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Were you having an affair?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.82,1:31:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇. 哇   你说了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Wow. Wow, you just said it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.82,1:31:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还准备再绕上半小时呢\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I was expecting to dance around this for another half-hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.33,1:31:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见过他和这个女人在一起. 他和她调情. 他一直这样\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've seen him with women. He flirts. He always has.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.83,1:31:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从某种程度上看   我只是猜测...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And on some level, I just presumed that he was...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.84,1:31:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...他欺骗了我妈 但是我没有证据\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...cheating on my mom. I just never had proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.34,1:31:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能问个问题吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.34,1:31:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你找到了契约   为什么不问艾迪?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If you found this deed, why didn't you just ask Eddie?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.85,1:31:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他快死了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Because he's dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.36,1:31:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看   我不知道你瞭解多少情况\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Look, I don't know how much you want to know about any of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.86,1:32:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对你父亲有印象...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You have one image of your father...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.36,1:32:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...我不应该改变它...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and it'd be wrong of me to change it...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.87,1:32:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...尤其是在游戏的结尾\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...especially this late in the game.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.87,1:32:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲说了他从来没说过的事...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}My father talked about things he never did...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.37,1:32:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...我相信这些他从没有说过\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and I'm sure he did a lot of things that he never talked about.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.88,1:32:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试着在两者之间找到共同点\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm just trying to reconcile the two.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.38,1:32:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先你要瞭解...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The first thing you have to understand...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.88,1:32:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...你父亲没想到会来这\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...is that your father never meant to end up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.39,1:32:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而他来了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Yet he did.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.89,1:32:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两次\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Twice.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.89,1:32:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次   他来早了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The first time, he was early.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.89,1:32:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次   他来晚了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The second time, he was late.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.90,1:32:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些日子  你父亲为自己工作\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Those days, your father was working for himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.90,1:32:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华.布鲁是这样一个人...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If there's one thing you could say about Edward Bloom...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.40,1:32:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...他是个喜欢社交的人   大家都喜欢和他说话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...it's that he was a social person, and people took a liking to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.41,1:32:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天晚上   他出门三周后回来...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}One night, he was returning from three weeks on the road...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.41,1:32:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,... 遇上了从没碰到过的暴风雨\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...when he hit a thunderstorm unlike any in his life.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.01,1:34:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运就是喜欢捉弄人...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Fate has a way of circling back on a man...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.52,1:34:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...让他大吃一惊\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and taking him by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.52,1:34:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人在生命的各种时段看事物角度也是不同的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A man sees things differently at different times in his life.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.03,1:35:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个镇在年老的他看来已经不同了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This town didn't seem the same now that he was older.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.53,1:35:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一条新路已经把外面的世界带进了幽灵镇...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A new road had brought the outside world to Spectre...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.04,1:35:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...随之而来的是  银行  抵押和债务\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and with it, banks, liens and debt.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.54,1:35:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你看的到的地方   就有人破产\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Almost everywhere you looked, people were bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.54,1:35:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天为幽灵镇举行一次拍卖\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The auction today is for the town of Spectre.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.05,1:35:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-开价 $1 0  000. -於是爱德华.布鲁...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- The opening bid will be $ 10,000. - So Edward Bloom...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.05,1:35:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-...决定买下这个镇 -50  000.\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...decided to buy the town. - 50,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.56,1:35:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不能相信我的眼睛-- -他从来不是个有钱的人...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I couldn't believe my eyes... - He was never a wealthy man...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.06,1:35:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...但是他能让别人变的有钱   现在他找他们帮忙\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...but he had made other men rich, and now he asked for their favors.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.07,1:35:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我决定存.... -他们中的大多数人没见过幽灵镇\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- I'm trying to save... - Most of them hadn't seen Spectre.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.57,1:35:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是听爱德华描述过\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They only had Edward's words to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.57,1:35:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这些已经够了. 他卖了出去\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's all he needed. He sold them on the dream.
