Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.11,1:45:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和你妈妈在楼上 还有本耐特大夫\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's upstairs with your mom and Dr. Bennett.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.61,1:45:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会好吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Is he gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.12,1:45:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't suppose that I could...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.12,1:45:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...应该留下来. 我的意思是   假如....\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...stay here with him. I mean, in case...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.62,1:45:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如他醒了   我应该在这里\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}In case he wakes up, I really ought to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.63,1:45:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我留下来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.13,1:45:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和傑瑟芬回家吧. 我陪夜\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Why don't you go home with Josephine. I'll stay tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.13,1:45:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好吗? -好\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Is that okay? - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.64,1:46:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威尔  如果有事打电话...?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Will, you'll call if there's any...?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.14,1:46:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道. 知道了. 我会打的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I will. I will. I'll call.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.64,1:46:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你想和爸爸呆会吗? -是的.谢谢\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Do you want some time with Dad? - Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.71,1:47:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴看见你不是来真心谈话的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Glad to see you're not trying to have a heartfelt talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.21,1:47:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最烦的一件事就是...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}One of my greatest annoyances is when...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.22,1:47:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...和不想听的人倾诉\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...people try to talk to those who can't hear them.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.22,1:47:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有优势\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, we have an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.72,1:47:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和父亲从来不说话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}My father and I never talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.73,1:47:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲告诉过你关於你出生那天的事吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Your father ever tell you about the day you were born?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.73,1:47:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对   1000多次了. 他抓住了那条抓不到的鱼的事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Yeah, a thousand times. He caught an uncatchable fish.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.23,1:47:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个. 真实的故事. 他和你说了吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Not that. The real story. He ever tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.74,1:47:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.74,1:47:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲下午3点进来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Well, your mother came in about 3 in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.25,1:47:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的邻居送她进来的   考虑到你父亲外出威齐塔...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Her neighbor drove her, on account of your father was away on business...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.75,1:47:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...做生意的情况\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...in Wichita.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.25,1:48:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早产了一个星期   不过非常顺利\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You were born a week early, but there were no complications.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.25,1:48:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接生非常成功. 你父亲很遗憾没在场\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It was a perfect delivery. Your father was sorry not to be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.26,1:48:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那时男人都不进产房...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But it wasn't the custom then for men to be in the room for deliveries...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.26,1:48:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...所以我不明白他在场的话会有多少不同\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...so I can't see how it would've been much different had he been there.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.77,1:48:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你出生的真实故事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And that's the real story of how you were born.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.27,1:48:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很有意思   对吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Not very exciting, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.78,1:48:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能在真实的版本...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And I suppose if I had to choose between the true version...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.78,1:48:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...和关於鱼和婚戒的精美故事...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and an elaborate one involving a fish and a wedding ring...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.28,1:48:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...做出选择\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...I might choose the fancy version.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.29,1:48:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是   那是我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But, then that's just me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.29,1:48:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的版本\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I kind of liked your version.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.31,1:49:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.81,1:49:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿   爸爸? 嘿  你要我去叫护士?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hey, Dad? Hey, you want me to get the nurse?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.32,1:49:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要什么? 我能做什么? 要我拿什么?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What do you want? What can I do? What can I get?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.82,1:49:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要喝水?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You want some water?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.83,1:49:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要点水?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You want a bit of water?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.33,1:49:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The river.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.33,1:49:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The river?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.84,1:49:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我发生了什么\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tell me how it happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.84,1:49:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么发生的?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How what happens?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.84,1:49:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How I go.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.35,1:49:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是当你看到那个眼睛的时候?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You mean what you saw in The Eye?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.87,1:50:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那个故事  爸爸. 你没告诉过我\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't know that story, Dad. You never told me that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.37,1:50:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好. 嘿   好的   我试试\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Okay. Hey, okay, I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.37,1:50:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你帮忙. 告诉我怎么开始\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I need your help. Tell me how it starts.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.38,1:50:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.38,1:50:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的. 好的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.89,1:50:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的   在早上...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Okay, so it's in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.39,1:50:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...我和你在医院的时候睡着了. 我醒来...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and you and I are in the hospital, and I've fallen asleep. And I wake up...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.89,1:50:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...看着你   你看上去好多了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and I see you, and somehow you're better.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.90,1:50:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.90,1:50:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不一样了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're different.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.90,1:50:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-爸爸 -我们离开这吧\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Dad. - Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.90,1:50:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说:\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Then I say:
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.40,1:50:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸   你不能--\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Dad, you're in no condition...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.91,1:50:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把轮椅拿来\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Get that wheelchair.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.91,1:50:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快!我们没多少时间了!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hurry up! We haven't much time!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.91,1:50:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦下了楼   我们就畅通无阻了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Once we get off this floor, we're in the clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.41,1:50:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们坐上轮椅...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And we get in the wheelchair...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.42,1:51:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快点! -...就像我们在逃离医院一样\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Faster! ...like we're escaping the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.92,1:51:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.92,1:51:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绕过了本耐特大夫   他想拦住我们\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We pass Dr. Bennett, who tries to slow us down.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.42,1:51:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-拦住他们! -我们飞奔过大厅\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Stop them! - We're flying down the hall.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.43,1:51:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安在追我们\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Orderly after orderly is chasing us.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.93,1:51:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和傑瑟芬在最后\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mom and Josephine are at the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.93,1:51:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间解释了! 拦住他们!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No time to explain! Stall them!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.44,1:51:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们飞奔过围栏...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We come flying out over the curb...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.44,1:51:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...你的旧款红色车停在那. 不过很新. 崭新的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and your old red Charger is there. But it's new. Brand-new.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.45,1:51:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带你上去...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And I pick you up...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.45,1:51:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...你几乎没什么重量. 我不能解释\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and somehow you hardly weigh anything. I can't explain it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.45,1:51:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开! 我们不需要!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Leave it! We don't need it!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.46,1:51:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水. 我要喝水\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Water. I need water.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.97,1:51:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们去哪? -河那里\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Where are we going? - The river.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.97,1:52:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走格伦镇这条路避免交通拥挤...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And we have to take Glenville to avoid traffic...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.47,1:52:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...因为去教堂的人开的很慢\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...because the damn church people drive too slow.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.52,1:52:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们越来越接近河...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And as we get close to the river...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.03,1:53:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在那!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's here!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.53,1:53:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...我们看见所有人都在那\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...we see that everybody is already there.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.05,1:53:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.05,1:53:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...所有人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.56,1:53:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不可思议了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.07,1:53:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生命的故事\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The story of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.58,1:53:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的是   他们看上去并不生气\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The strange thing is, there's not a sad face to be found.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.58,1:54:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都很高兴见到你...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Everyone is just so glad to see you...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.58,1:54:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...为你送行\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...and send you off right.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.59,1:54:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家再见! 别了! 再见!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Goodbye, everybody! Farewell! Adieu!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.60,1:54:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我河里的姑娘\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}My girl in the river.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.67,1:55:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变回到了原来的你\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You become what you always were.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.18,1:55:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一条大鱼\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A very big fish.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.68,1:55:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么发生的\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And that's how it happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.69,1:55:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.19,1:55:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太对了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.73,1:56:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.31,1:58:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的牧师做了主   我不能再要求什么了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The Lord is my shepherd, I shall not be in want.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.82,1:58:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他让我躺在碧绿的草地里\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He makes me to lie down in green pastures.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.32,1:58:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在清清的河水边\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He leads me beside the quiet waters.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.32,1:58:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他保留了我的灵魂\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He restores my soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.82,1:58:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他用他的名义引导我走向公正\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He guides me in the paths of righteousness for his name's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.33,1:58:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对   我走过了死亡的阴影...\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Yea, though I walk through the valley of the shadow of death...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:28.83,1:58:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...不再害怕恶魔   因为你和我在一起\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}...I will fear no evil, for you are with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.34,1:58:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善良和爱在我生命中的每一天\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Surely goodness and love will follow me all the days of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.88,1:59:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听到过那种听了几遍都不知道哪好笑的笑话吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Have you ever heard a joke so many times you've forgotten why it's funny?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.39,1:59:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你再听一遍觉得又是一个新的笑话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And then you hear it again and suddenly it's new.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.89,1:59:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你记得为什么第一次会喜欢它\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You remember why you loved it in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.89,1:59:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说他会和一个身高15英尺的巨人作战!\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So he said he'll fight the giant who was 15 feet tall!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.90,1:59:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-没门! -爸爸! 那是真的   对吗?\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- No way! - Dad! That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.90,1:59:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太对了\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.40,1:59:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧? 他确实是个巨人\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}See? So he was a giant.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.41,1:59:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜那是我父亲最后的笑话\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That was my father's final joke, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.41,1:59:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个讲了无数故事的人最终成了故事的一部分\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}A man tells his stories so many times that he becomes the stories.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:57.41,2:00:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事在他死后继续流传\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They live on after him.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.42,2:00:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这方面来看   他永远不死\N{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}And in that way, he becomes immortal.
